## Quick start
1. `pip install -r requirements.txt`  
2. `streamlit run app.py`  
3. On Home page paste your OpenAI API Key (session-only) or set `OPENAI_API_KEY` in environment/Secrets.
4. Go to **Greek Deities** â†’ choose figure â†’ Fetch related works â†’ select thumbnail â†’ view detail in **Works & Analysis**.

